name: Unidentified_human_assassin
content: A human assassin worked for the criminal syndicate Crimson Dawn during the Galactic Civil War. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, the assassin was present on the planet Garel when General Skarhorn delivered a speech to mark the opening of an Imperial munitions factory. The assassin managed to acquire an All Terrain Scout Transport which they used to threaten the general as he made his speech. The Imperial officer Beilert Valance was able to thwart the assassin by using a speeder bike to bring the walker down, which ultimately resulted in the assassin's death. Despite the assassins failure to kill Skarhorn, a second assassin was able to successfully kill the general.
